  "name": "Grasping Snare",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You rig vines and ropes to hold a creature in place. The first creature to enter the square must attempt a @Check[type:reflex|dc:26] save, with the following effects.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes a -5-foot status penalty to its Speed for 1 minute or until it Escapes (DC 26).</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is immobilized for 1 round, then takes a -5-foot status penalty to its Speed for 1 minute. Both effects end early if it Escapes (DC 26).</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is immobilized for 1 minute or until it Escapes (DC 26).</p>"
